  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.amidst.core.utils.KeyCompoundVector<E>

    public class KeyCompoundVector<E>
extends Object
implements MomentParameters, NaturalParameters, SufficientStatistics, Serializable
    This class implements the interfaces MomentParameters, NaturalParameters, and SufficientStatistics. It handles some key compound vector utility methods.
